    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Loius answer is correct, I just want to add an example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>listOne.add(\"A\");\nlistOne.add(\"B\");\nlistOne.add(\"C\");\n\nlistTwo.add(\"D\");\nlistTwo.add(\"E\");\nlistTwo.add(\"F\");      \n\nboolean noElementsInCommon = Collections.disjoint(listOne, listTwo); // true\n</code></pre>\n"
