    "body" : "<p><a href=\"https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/current/javadoc-api/org/springframework/util/CollectionUtils.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">org.springframework.util.CollectionUtils</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>boolean containsAny(java.util.Collection&lt;?&gt; source, java.util.Collection&lt;?&gt; candidates)\n\nReturn true if any element in 'candidates' is contained in 'source'; otherwise returns false\n</code></pre>\n"
