    "body" : "<p>With <strong><code>java 8</code></strong>, we can do like below to check if one list contains any element of other list<br></p>\n\n<pre><code>boolean var = lis1.stream().filter(element -&gt; list2.contains(element)).findFirst().isPresent();\n</code></pre>\n"
